---
globs: components/**/*.tsx
---
- One component per file, named export only (no default exports).
- Props interface defined in the component file itself.
- No fetch, no SDK calls, no business logic inside components.
- No useEffect for data fetching — data arrives via props from the parent page.
- If file exceeds ~150 lines, split it.
- Structure order: imports → props interface → hooks → derived values → handlers → return.
- Mobile first: base styles → md: → lg:
- No fixed widths. Use w-full, max-w-*, flex, grid.
- Always handle loading, error, and empty states explicitly.
- Use shadcn/ui as base — do not rebuild what it already provides.
